// How an appointment was confirmed. Lets us tell "patient called us back"
// apart from "reception phoned the patient" вҖ” important for staff-load
// metrics and for routing inbound responses (SMS/TG) to the right handler.
enum ConfirmationVia {
  BOOKING_AUTO // Inbound: the patient created the booking themselves via PHONE/KIOSK.
  MANUAL_CRM // Reception/callcenter flipped CONFIRMED from the CRM UI.
  SMS_REPLY // Patient texted YES/Р”Рҗ/HA to a reminder SMS.
  TG_BUTTON // Patient pressed "РҹРҫРҙСӮРІРөСҖР¶РҙР°СҺ" on a Telegram reminder.
  INBOUND_CALL // Patient called us back to confirm вҖ” flipped by whoever picked up.
}

